{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/blog/alacritty-everywhere","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Some time ago I played with setting up <a href=\"/code/anaconda-in-vscode-terminal\">Anaconda in VS Code</a>, but this time I want to upgrade <a href=\"/code/customize-git-bash-for-windows\">Git for Windows</a> and run it from Alacritty.</p>\n<h2 id=\"shells\" style=\"position:relative;\">Shells<a href=\"#shells\" aria-label=\"shells permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"git\" style=\"position:relative;\">Git<a href=\"#git\" aria-label=\"git permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">D:\\Programs\\Alacritty-v0.13.2-portable.exe --command \"C:\\Program Files\\Git\\bin\\bash.exe\"</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"mingw\" style=\"position:relative;\">MinGW<a href=\"#mingw\" aria-label=\"mingw permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">D:\\Programs\\Alacritty-v0.13.2-portable.exe --command C:\\msys64\\msys2_shell.cmd -defterm -here -no-start -mingw64</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"msvc\" style=\"position:relative;\">MSVC<a href=\"#msvc\" aria-label=\"msvc permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h3>\n<p>This will not work because of the spaces (arrgh)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">D:\\Programs\\Alacritty-v0.13.2-portable.exe --command cmd.exe /k \"C:\\Program Files\\Microsoft Visual Studio\\2022\\Community\\Common7\\Tools\\VsDevCmd.bat\"\n\nD:\\Programs\\Alacritty-v0.13.2-portable.exe  --option shell=\"{program='cmd.exe',args=['/k C:\\Program Files\\Microsoft Visual Studio\\2022\\Community\\Common7\\Tools\\VsDevCmd.bat']}\"</code></pre></div>\n<p>But it works if you put it in the config <code class=\"language-text\">%appdata%\\alacritty\\alacritty.toml</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"toml\"><pre class=\"language-toml\"><code class=\"language-toml\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token table class-name\">shell</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token key property\">args</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'/k \"C:\\Program Files\\Microsoft Visual Studio\\2022\\Community\\Common7\\Tools\\VsDevCmd.bat\"'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token key property\">program</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"cmd.exe\"</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>A side note. If you get an error about changing only <code class=\"language-text\">shell.args</code> while <code class=\"language-text\">shell.program</code> is undefined, then this means that one need to set both arguments and use the proper types (I noticed that TOML's parser is very gentle and spaces are not allowed in the array syntax (I'm testing this on the latest Alacritty (0.13.2) that migrated to TOML format)). <a href=\"https://github.com/alacritty/alacritty/issues/6707\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">ref</a></p>\n<p>But maybe one shouldn't touch the <code class=\"language-text\">shell</code> option because there's a special <code class=\"language-text\">command</code> option.</p>\n<h3 id=\"conda\" style=\"position:relative;\">Conda<a href=\"#conda\" aria-label=\"conda permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h3>\n<p>And here is an example when it works okay when the path has no spaces</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">D:\\Programs\\Alacritty-v0.13.2-portable.exe --command \"cmd.exe /k C:\\Users\\neupo\\miniconda3\\Scripts\\activate.bat\"</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"paths\" style=\"position:relative;\">Paths<a href=\"#paths\" aria-label=\"paths permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>where I added SSH agent autostart: <code class=\"language-text\">C:\\Program Files\\Git\\etc\\profile.d\\git-prompt.sh</code></li>\n<li>where I added <strong>.vim</strong> folder: <code class=\"language-text\">C:\\msys64\\home\\neupo</code></li>\n<li>where I added local <strong>bin</strong> folder to the PATH: <code class=\"language-text\">C:\\msys64\\home\\neupo\\.bash_profile</code></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-d</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"/c/Users/neupo/.cargo/bin\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">then</span>\n  <span class=\"token assign-left variable\"><span class=\"token environment constant\">PATH</span></span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"/c/Users/neupo/.cargo/bin:<span class=\"token variable\">${<span class=\"token environment constant\">PATH</span>}</span>\"</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">fi</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-d</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"/c/Users/neupo/.local/bin\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">then</span>\n    <span class=\"token assign-left variable\"><span class=\"token environment constant\">PATH</span></span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"/c/Users/neupo/.local/bin:<span class=\"token variable\">${<span class=\"token environment constant\">PATH</span>}</span>\"</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">fi</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"fonts-and-emoji\" style=\"position:relative;\">Fonts and emoji<a href=\"#fonts-and-emoji\" aria-label=\"fonts and emoji permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.nerdfonts.com/font-downloads\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Nerd Fonts</a>. My preferred choice is <a href=\"https://github.com/ryanoasis/nerd-fonts/releases/download/v3.4.0/SourceCodePro.zip\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Source Code Pro</a> (which is called <em>sauce</em> here)</p>\n<p>Font related settings in <strong>alacritty.toml</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"toml\"><pre class=\"language-toml\"><code class=\"language-toml\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token table class-name\">font</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token key property\">size</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">13.0</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token table class-name\">font.normal</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token key property\">family</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"SauceCodePro NF\"</span>\n<span class=\"token key property\">style</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Regular\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token table class-name\">font.bold</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token key property\">family</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"SauceCodePro NF\"</span>\n<span class=\"token key property\">style</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Bold\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token table class-name\">font.italic</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token key property\">family</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"SauceCodePro NF\"</span>\n<span class=\"token key property\">style</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Italic\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token table class-name\">font.bold_italic</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token key property\">family</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"SauceCodePro NF\"</span>\n<span class=\"token key property\">style</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Bold Italic\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>If you see <code class=\"language-text\">font FontDesc {...} not found</code> then it's time to update the Windows font cache, close terminal, install all Windows updates, reboot your computer, reinstall video driver and all other shaman steps:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"powershell\"><pre class=\"language-powershell\"><code class=\"language-powershell\"><span class=\"token function\">Restart-Service</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>Name FontCache</code></pre></div>\n<p>Also an option to install all of them <a href=\"https://gist.github.com/stramel/658d702f3af8a86a6fe8b588720e0e23\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">with a script</a></p>\n<p>Configure your terminal for better experience (color emoji) <a href=\"https://github.com/alacritty/alacritty/issues/153#issuecomment-630636358\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://github.com/alacritty/alacritty/issues/153#issuecomment-630636358</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://fonts.google.com/noto/specimen/Noto+Color+Emoji\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://fonts.google.com/noto/specimen/Noto+Color+Emoji</a></p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">C:\\msys64\\mingw64\\etc\\fonts\\conf.d</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;alias>\n\t&lt;family>monoscpace&lt;/family>\n\t&lt;prefer>\n\t&lt;family>Cousine&lt;/family> &lt;!-- Your preferred monospace font -->\n\t&lt;family>Noto Color Emoji&lt;/family> &lt;!-- Your preferred emoji font -->\n\t&lt;/prefer>\n&lt;/alias></code></pre></div>","excerpt":"Some time ago I played with setting up Anaconda in VS Code, but this time I want to upgrade Git for Windows and run it from Alacritty…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#shells\">Shells</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#git\">Git</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#mingw\">MinGW</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#msvc\">MSVC</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#conda\">Conda</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#paths\">Paths</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#fonts-and-emoji\">Fonts and emoji</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"socialcard":"gatsby-plugin-social-card/1162d8cf-dc8c-5d3a-bf38-969825afe19d.jpg"},"frontmatter":{"date":"August 25, 2024","published":"August 25, 2024","lastModified":"July 12, 2025","title":"Alacritty everywhere","subtitle":"My default terminal emulator on Windows","section":null,"draft":null,"developing":null,"buttonText":null,"buttonLink":null,"secondButtonText":null,"secondButtonLink":null,"featuredImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"showLikes":true,"absolutePath":"/home/runner/work/mikolasan.github.io/mikolasan.github.io/src/markdown/blog/alacritty-everywhere.md","url":"/blog/alacritty-everywhere","next":{"excerpt":"When humans create real artificial intelligence, will it need sleep? This was my thought just before I fell asleep. I was thinking about Lex…","fileAbsolutePath":"/home/runner/work/mikolasan.github.io/mikolasan.github.io/src/markdown/blog/should-ai-sleep.md","frontma